{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "4bbbaf99-cd1b-406b-942e-22df9dc9992d", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/4bbbaf99-cd1b-406b-942e-22df9dc9992d@2.pkg/1772597578896/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597579527", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/4bbbaf99-cd1b-406b-942e-22df9dc9992d@2.pkg/1772597578896/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597579527"}, "identifier": "4bbbaf99-cd1b-406b-942e-22df9dc9992d", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①不符合题意：题干是国台办对“台独”顽固分子沈伯洋关联企业予以惩戒，并未提及受到法律制裁。</p>\n\n<p>②错误：维护国家利益是每个公民的基本义务，并非基本权利。</p>\n\n<p>③④正确：题干中的惩戒措施是维护国家主权和两岸同胞根本利益的正义之举，说明维护国家统一和领土完整是人间正道，实现国家统一是中华儿女的共同愿望，符合题意。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）2025年6月6日，国台办宣布对“台独”顽固分子沈伯洋关联企业予以惩戒。惩戒措施是对“台独”分裂势力的严正警告和有力震慑，是维护国家主权和两岸同胞根本利益的正义之举。材料说明了（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①一切“台独”行为都将受到法律制裁</p>\n\n<p>②维护国家利益是每个公民的基本权利</p>\n\n<p>③维护国家统一和领土完整是人间正道</p>\n\n<p>④实现国家统一是中华儿女的共同愿望</p>\n", "title": "（原创）2025年6月6日，国台办宣布对“台独”顽固分子沈伯洋关联企业予以惩戒。惩戒措施是对“台独”分裂势力的严正警告和有力震慑，是维护国家主权和两岸同胞根本利益的正义之举。材料说明了（   ）①一切“台独”行为都将受到法律制裁②维护国家利益是每个公民的基本权利③维护国家统一和领土完整是人间正道④实现国家统一是中华儿女的共同愿望", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/4bbbaf99-cd1b-406b-942e-22df9dc9992d@2.pkg/item.json?v=1755183005025", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（原创）2025年6月6日，国台办宣布对“台独”顽固分子沈伯洋关联企业予以惩戒。惩戒措施是对“台独”分裂势力的严正警告和有力震慑，是维护国家主权和两岸同胞根本利益的正义之举。材料说明了（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①一切“台独”行为都将受到法律制裁</p>\n\n<p>②维护国家利益是每个公民的基本权利</p>\n\n<p>③维护国家统一和领土完整是人间正道</p>\n\n<p>④实现国家统一是中华儿女的共同愿望</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "4bbbaf99-cd1b-406b-942e-22df9dc9992d", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（原创）2025年6月6日，国台办宣布对“台独”顽固分子沈伯洋关联企业予以惩戒。惩戒措施是对“台独”分裂势力的严正警